4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals seeking to become cybersecurity specialists, with no prior experience required. Over a 16-week period, students participate in 3 live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 18. The program focuses on essential skills such as Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management through data loss prevention. Students can choose to learn in English or Spanish. Upon completion, participants earn an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by multiple institutions. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop